title: Dakine Section Wet/Dry Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Section Pack in the Timber print.
Pack Features:
- Waterproof roll top wetsuit pocket
- Insulated cooler pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Tarp wax pocket
- Water bottle pocket
- Stealth shoulder strap bottle opener
- Two waterproof zippered pockets
